<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation - RoomCtrl</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #1f1f1f;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 30px 20px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #d72f3f;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #666;
            flex: 1;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .participants-section {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .participants-header {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .participant {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-left: 3px solid #d72f3f;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #1B2532;
            color: #cccccc;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
        }
        a {
            color: #d72f3f;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Booking Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{ user.firstName }},</p>
            
            <p>Your room booking has been confirmed! Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div class="booking-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Meeting Title:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ booking.title }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Room:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ room.roomName }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Location:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ room.location }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Start Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ booking.startedAt|date('d/m/Y H:i', 'Europe/Warsaw') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">End Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ booking.endedAt|date('d/m/Y H:i', 'Europe/Warsaw') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Expected Participants:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ booking.participantsCount }}</span>
                </div>
                
                {% if participants|length > 0 %}
                <div class="participants-section">
                    <div class="participants-header">Invited Participants:</div>
                    {% for participant in participants %}
                    <div class="participant">
                        {{ participant.firstName }} {{ participant.lastName }} ({{ participant.email }})
                    </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            
            <p>Please note that the organizer will send invitations to the participants. You can manage your booking anytime through the RoomCtrl application.</p>
            
            <p>If you need to cancel or modify this booking, please do so as soon as possible to ensure other participants are notified in time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This message was sent automatically. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 RoomCtrl. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
